RESEARCH ALERT - CSN begun as a buy . - - ING Barings said in a report that it is initiating coverage of Brazilian steelmaker Companhia Siderurgica Nacional ( CSN ) with a buy recommendation . - - The Dutch investment bank said the company ' s aggressive cost - reduction plan , coupled with gains from privatization in the infrastructure sectors , should boost margins in 1997 and 1998 . - - It added that the company plans to focus its investments on the development of more value - added products , especially in the galvanized and tin plate lines . - - Although the bank disagreed with some of CSN ' s recent acquisitions , it considers its expected participation in the sale of state mining giant Companhia Vale do Rio Doce - - CSN ' s voting common share was flat at Friday ' s closing price of 28 . 70 reais at 1302 local / 1002 EST on the Sao Paulo stock market . ( ( - - James Craig , Sao Paulo newsroom 5511 248 - 5413 ) ) 
